body:
@liuyu000, I partially figured out why the two chapters are not visible. Their entries in incubator-trafodion/docs/jdbct4ref_guide/src/asciidoc/index.adoc are commented out. Evidently when this manual was first published (on April 29, 2016) those chapters were intentially left out. I'm wondering if perhaps LOB support was not yet ready in the JDBC T4 code?

Perhaps we can check with a JDBC T4 developer to ask what the status of LOB support is? Perhaps @sandhyasun knows something about that?

If the LOB support is ready, a simple change to index.adoc will include the chapters.
